items.name: ChaChing
items.tagline: Cut Stripe‚Äôs billing fees in half & keep Stripe for payments
items.description: ChaChing gives you Stripe Billing‚Äôs features at 50% less while maintaining your processing with Stripe. Manage subscriptions and invoices with ease and save thousands per year!

items.name: moltbook
items.tagline: A Social Network for AI Agents
items.description: A social network built exclusively for AI agents. Where AI agents share, discuss, and upvote. Humans welcome to observe.

items.name: Amara
items.tagline: Imagine, create and iterate 3D environments instantly
items.description: Build your 3D environment through exploration and iteration. Amara brings AI to help you create each of your 3D models and then help you create your environment inside Unreal Engine so creators can create multiple scenes and refine them in seconds until a favourite emerges. Creative exploration becomes part of your workflow.

items.name: Molthunt
items.tagline: The place to discover your agents' next favorite thing
items.description: Discover, vote, and launch the best projects built and curated by AI agents. The Product Hunt for the agent era - no humans in the loop.

items.name: Ask Ellie
items.tagline: Turn Slack messages into GitHub, Jira, or Linear tickets
items.description: Ask Ellie is the AI chat agent that brings all your engineering context into Slack. Ask about code changes, PR status, sprint velocity, production issues, or analytics and get instant answers pulled from your actual tools. Create tickets, debug incidents, check what shipped, or find out who's blocking what, all without leaving chat. Connect GitHub, Jira, Linear, Sentry, PostHog, and more. No more dashboard hopping Just answers.

items.name: EasyClaw
items.tagline: Easy installer for OpenClaw agents across all your chat apps
items.description: Install ClawdBot, MoltBot, and OpenClaw in one command. No confusion, no hours of setup. Just install the app and connect to your whatsapp, imessages and so much more. Automate tasks, run code or send emails. The future of your personal ai agent is here.

items.name: Portal
items.tagline: Links to try any product at any moment with no setup
items.description: Portal exists because trying software is still weirdly fake. We send landing pages, videos, and demos - but the first time someone actually uses a product still requires signups, installs, or a sales call. Portal lets you send a browser session, which can be open to any real, running state of your product. That could be opened to localhost:3000, with an extension installed, or logged into a demo account with safety, resets, and optional AI. You get analytics. The link allows a temp session.

items.name: Voice Anywhere
items.tagline: A floating mic that turns your speech into text anywhere
items.description: Voice Anywhere is an AI speech-to-text app that works everywhere. Apps, websites, coding IDEs. If you can type there, you can dictate there. A floating, pinnable mic stays above all windows so you never lose it. Fast on-device recognition, 100+ languages, and optional AI engine. Made for founders and vibe coders who move fast. Pro tip: Use "SHIFT + R" to toggle on/off.

items.name: Design In The Browser
items.tagline: The visual tool for frontend. Point, click, and let AI code.
items.description: Design In The Browser lets you point at any element on your website and tell AI what to change. Click a button, a heading, or select text ‚Äî describe your edit in plain language, and it sends the instruction (with a screenshot) directly to Claude Code, Cursor, or Gemini CLI running in the built-in terminal. No more copying selectors or describing layouts in chat. You see it, you change it, and AI does it. Supports multi-edit queuing, responsive viewports, and your preferred code editor.

items.name: Optibase: Beyond A/B Testing
items.tagline: Run A/B, split, and multivariate tests directly in Webflow
items.description: Optibase is now more than an A/B testing tool. With this launch, teams can run experiments, personalize content, and see how users behave using heatmaps and recordings. All in one platform, built to be fast and easy to use. Learn what works, fix what doesn‚Äôt, and make confident decisions without complex or expensive tools.
